Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come at me from any direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.39,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, we have a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, fulfill the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I realize that this has to be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact that I am having this dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means I may be harboring expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan is generating\Na Zero-G magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity within this room\Nis now under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuta, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.03,0:01:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current mobility is too limited\Nto evade attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Magical Devil Girl in Pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life function critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your roller shoes are banned\Nfor the foreseeable future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what you get for\Nputting a hole in my ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right! I obtained\Na permit from the Committee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gasp! Did they have a hand in this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I must hurry before\Nthe situation becomes dire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either her chunibyo is getting worse,\Nor she's having a relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may fulfill our contract as we see fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I hadn't said all that to her,\Nby now we'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no! Not, not, not, not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka and I aren't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said what I said because\NI thought it was the right solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mobility confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked One gale force heroic blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Am I the enemy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will summon the Dark Flame Dragon within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:03:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Flame Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a mutation of the Black Flame Dragon having gained dark powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the source of the\NDark Flame Master's powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it is your dragon soulmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you need it right this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Enemy approaches.\NI believe her to be a powerful magic user.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic user? Do you mean Toka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I have already imprisoned\Nthe Priestess within the Vatican...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the might of my dark powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make her mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic user is even more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear this person is one of the demon elite...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and so I must summon the Dark Flame Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my T-shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical injection is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I order you, on the name of\NWicked Lord Shingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dark Flame Dragon sleeping\Nwithin this man! Appear before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Don't draw\Nsummoning circles on my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which actually looks pretty damned good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, suit up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least I'd like to refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I appreciate the effort this took.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just put it on either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I will put it on if you get\Nbetter marks than me on the next test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get worse marks, the Dark Flame Dragon\Nwill be confined. Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that 'cheh'!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you the might of\NWicked Lord Shingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in a way you will not soon forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.18,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,YUTA TOGASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.35,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,RIKKA TAKANASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're nearly identical!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet! Now you are servant to a servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you are awesome! My fervor is renewed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, you really worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must now produce the Dark Flame Dragon\Nthat resides within you for my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you will wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it is a magical girl costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had to wear a T-shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully picky for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did a magical girl costume\Nenter the equation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Flame Dragon\Nresponds powerfully to magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, the act of wrapping\Nyour entire body in magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will prompt it to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I designed it to flatter you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dekomori and I co-produced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a true tour de force!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Through the all-seeing\NWicked Lord Shingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have measured your waist, hips and bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware that I'm a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the unfortunate fact that\Nthere are no male magical girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...its production was fraught with difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I have prepared this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin tails?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, your transformation call\Nis personalized just for you: "Brave Up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, transform at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumin-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! A deal is a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you removing your clothing?!\NYou must transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen? Let's see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it isn't bad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come wish with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, a flawless parabola.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that to my phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy moley! Nibutani putting the moves\Non Togashi in drag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, have you finished your transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really good on you. I am relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, speak the incantation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so cute, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, have you joined them, Kumin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deko just happened to have this prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.91,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Far-East Magical Napping\N Society Summer Thereof
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! The angel! I'm here to make war!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears I am summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell from that announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, for I am an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deep black fallen angel to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I have been\Nservant to a fallen angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a good development! Very smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take my leave. Please exercise caution, Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you what kind of angels we can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan detection mode activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Location: the vicinity of the intercom room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's angelic about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who was that on the intercom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:38.28,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERCOM ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will look in this direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial breakaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, are you a surviving angel,\Nor are you a new kind of angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you have perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sophia Ring SP Saturn VII!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the magical devil girl Sophia\Nthe whole town is talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am otherwise known as "she who rules\Nthe devilish magical seven holy lands!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do well to remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Wicked Lord Shingan,\Nthe deep black fallen angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rikka Takanashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are the Wicked Lord Shingan?\NI could not ask for a better opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, let us commence the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Wicked Lord Shingan, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Field, deploy!\NImprisoned King Containment Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Lord, recognized.\NMagical power, released.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be destroyed, real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherubim aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow up, synapses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim, descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banishment This World!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndrilical metaphysical!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an impressive display of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are definitely the angel I took you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense an unpleasant premonition\Nfrom you. So you must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Split open, Door of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release the darkness within.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Utilize the power of the King of Demise\Nto scatter the fictitious ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The ultimate magic so soon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and conduct me to the finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schwarz Aschenputtel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vulcanus Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shield was improvised,\Nbut that was real power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very clever, fallen angel Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophia just may have to take off\Nthe kid gloves with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, but I am a magical devil girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...quite unlike your typical\Npowder-puff magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many of my Thousand Phoenix\Ndo you think you can dodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firebird Flame Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overconfidence is your own worst enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A marionette?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity system, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Vermillion Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entwine the darkness and become dark flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Aria magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be entombed in the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onyx Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suppressive defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shichimiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't enter a school\Nyou don't attend without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satone Shichimiya is a girl I hung out with\Nin Year One of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of fact, she is the Patient Zero\Nwho caused my chunibyo outbreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the way she spoke,\Nsaw her in invisible combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...decided it was awesome, and imitated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, both the Dark Flame Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and "Be enveloped in the flames\Nof darkness and disappear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...both sort of came from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is great. Is this your hideout, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, that one is dangerous. Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to resume our battle,\NDeep Black Fallen Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Shichimiya, in her chunibyo way,\Ndecided that Rikka is a fallen angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll make you regret ever picking a fight with Sophia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then deduced from her uniform which school\Nshe attends, and came to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll show you the power of a magical devil girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew she had taken a turn for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you out next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I have to go home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana told me to walk Shichimiya home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, we will celebrate our
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,reunion by raising a glass to the posthumous world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, but only with juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later! You really haven't\Nchanged a bit, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised trackers from the\NOrganization were still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should exercise caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be straight with you.\NI'm through with all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean you're moving up from\NLevel 7 to a Level 8 hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's over, finished, done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more fires of darkness\Nand no more Dark Flame Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a distinctive feeling of deja vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, did you look into the angel's eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I am not a hero anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am an average Year Two high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Actually, I haven't been called "hero"\Nin more than three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That sounds boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boring? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring because it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is such a big, interesting place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you? We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take this train?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And get off here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And cross this bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live right above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So the Togashi nameplate is yours, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you living with Wicked Lord Shingan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Vermillion Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entwine the darkness and become dark flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be entombed in the abyss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onyx Flame Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan ultimate magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purgatorial Fascination!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purgatorial fascination...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is one of Wicked Lord Shingan's\Neight deep secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is his most powerful attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A provisional magical devil girl such as\Nyourself could not possibly resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-oh, I get it. Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Master! That is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. How is that a magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a commando girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, magic is used\Nto make people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits who manipulate magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were always thoroughly pure of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They never resorted to brute force...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memo, memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer, you're very knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will help to know thy enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to write this down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop taking notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the magical girl stuff anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the secret organization's hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's suspicious. Very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya... Shichimiya who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she and Togashi used to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Rikka suddenly\Nstarted fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be his ex?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you never can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She goes to another school\Nbut stormed into our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then went home with Togashi, right?\NThere's something to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the scene of the crime! A love triangle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morisummer, you're very bloodthirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop calling me Morisummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I really don't think it will come to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on Wicked Lord Shingan\Nthat I will never give in to the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuzuha. Have you forgotten about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, it's you, Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! How did you get so tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years.\NYou haven't changed much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll be the size\Nof a demonic non-articulated-foot worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Non-articulated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta! I have returned to base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I urgently require supplies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not anticipate she would infiltrate this easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually believe I would be\Nstopped by such a weak barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not underestimate\Nthe power of Sophia's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair! Why only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka, go put your bag away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya's folks are going to be\Nlate home from work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so she'll be eating supper with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it, we can settle here and now\Nwho is the superior magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow. That's very effective, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satone, you used to always hang out\Nwith Yuta back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I required a Hero's abilities\Nto locate the samsara corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought\NI would find his base here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichimiya, I forget.\NYou didn't know where I lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that even though we were allies, you could
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never trust me with that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made several attempts to shadow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would always warn me\Nwhen we left for school in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to be extra cautious\Nbecause we might be followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why is Wicked Lord Shingan living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel no need to disclose that to my foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rikka originally lived in the apartment above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she found herself homeless by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So you are a wanderer\Nwithout a base in the mundane world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-no, all dark beings are this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I frequently spend time of\Nnon-existence in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only took up residence here\Ndue to my contract with Yuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is merely transitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one haughty freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A contract through Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been joined for many moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really a contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It is merely a contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It is not as commonplace as\Nmerely "going out."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And besides, Kuzuha is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found a travelling partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's the all-powerful Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. I get it, so back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked Lord Shingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal with Hero?\NWhat is your objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My original goal was to discover\Nthe invisible boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have already achieved that objective\Nwith our combined strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, my current objective is to awaken
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe Dark Flame Dragon sleeping within him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall needing any such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do. Your spirit-soul demands it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Flame Dragon? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you, Wicked Lord Shingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, I should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sophia needs to prepare herself\Nfor battle with the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, Shichimiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Kuzuha I said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in high school now,\Nso stop being so clingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come? We always used to touch noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's banned! Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did say goodbye to you\Nwhen I left, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did say anything to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I transferred schools. I just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because that would be goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you say your farewells,\Nthat becomes goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you lived somewhere in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was never goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is never goodbye until you say farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the logic of the world,\Nand one of the natural laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will remain unchanged for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is how I was reunited\Nwith Satone Shichimiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always had that habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a greeting to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll enter into a contract with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never go near any girl but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, safe in my anxious certainty\Nthat new trouble had yet to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was filled with careless joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I was one step closer to Rikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
